{"title":"fastApi项目","uid":"5c72a5823c895d1bf5e00cfab1495779","slug":"fastApi项目","date":"2025-12-24T02:23:21.000Z","updated":"2026-01-09T07:32:05.588Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/fastApi项目.json","keywords":"AI、Python","cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"什么是FastApi\"><a href=\"#什么是FastApi\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什么是FastApi\"></a>什么是FastApi</h2><p>一个用于构建API的现代、快速的Web框架，快速构建api，异步架构，易于使用和学习，自动生产的交互式文档。原生异步支持，释放真正性。</p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767524127501.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<h3 id=\"同步和异步\"><a href=\"#同步和异步\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"同步和异步\"></a><strong>同步和异步</strong></h3><p>同步请求当出现I&#x2F;O阻塞时候，需等待I&#x2F;O操作完成在继续处理下一个请求，耗时较长</p>\n<p>异步请求当出现I&#x2F;O阻塞时，可以去执行其他的请求</p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767524516344.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767524537387.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767524571972.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>类型提示与验证</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767524708450.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<h2 id=\"路由分发\"><a href=\"#路由分发\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"路由分发\"></a>路由分发</h2><img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767525651700.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<p>路由  URL地址与处理函数之间的映射关系</p>\n<p><strong>参数简介和路径参数</strong></p>\n<p>参数就是客户端发送请求时附带的额外信息和指令，作用是让同一个接口能根据不同的输入，返回不同的输出结果</p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767525976003.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<p>路径参数 可以设置 对应的范围</p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767526227044.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767526992952.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767528019639.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n\n\n<p>请求体参数 </p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767528157008.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767528824925.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767529050524.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767529417484.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767529525068.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<p>中间件</p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767529746508.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767529854099.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767530138318.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767530206179.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n\n\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767530303262.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n\n\n<p><strong>依赖注入</strong></p>\n<p>可以让我们的视图函数在执行之前，先执行一段逻辑代码，这段逻辑代码可以返回新的值给视图函数</p>\n<p>就是将一些重复性的代码，单独写成依赖，在需要的视图函数中，注入这个依赖。</p>\n<p>使用场景：</p>\n<p>把公共的逻辑（比如处理分页参数、查询条件等）提取出来，让多个不同的 API 接口可以共享。</p>\n<p>共享业务逻辑、共享数据库连接</p>\n<p>实现安全、验证、角色权限 </p>\n<h2 id=\"restful风格的api\"><a href=\"#restful风格的api\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"restful风格的api\"></a>restful风格的api</h2><h2 id=\"ORM\"><a href=\"#ORM\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ORM\"></a>ORM</h2><p>ORM（Object-RelationalMapping,对象关系映射）是一种编程技术，用于在面向对象编程语言和关系型数据库之间建立映射。允许开发者通过操作对象的方式与数据库进行交互，而无需直接编写复杂的SQL语句。</p>\n<p>优势：</p>\n<p>减少重复的SQL代码</p>\n<p>代码更简洁易读</p>\n<p>自动处理数据库连接和事务</p>\n<p>防止SQL注入攻击</p>\n<p>ORM使用流程</p>\n<p>①安装</p>\n<p>②建库建表</p>\n<p>③操作数据</p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1767530666443.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Uvicorn 主要是用来运行fastapi的</p>\n<img src=\"/post/fastApi%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/QQ_1766543385841.png\" class=\"\" title=\"img\">\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"Pydantic-模型\"><a href=\"#Pydantic-模型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Pydantic 模型\"></a><code>Pydantic</code> 模型</h2><p><code>Pydantic</code>是一个基于 Python <strong>类型注解（type hints）</strong> 的：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>数据校验（validation）</li>\n<li>数据解析（parsing）</li>\n<li>数据序列化（serialization）</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>用类型定义数据结构，用模型自动校验和转换数据</strong></p></blockquote>\n","text":"什么是FastApi一个用于构建API的现代、快速的Web框架，快速构建api，异步架构，易于使用和学习，自动生产的交互式文档。原生异步支持，释放真正性。 同步...","permalink":"/post/fastApi项目","photos":[],"count_ti